<div id="outline-container-1" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="sec-1"><span class="section-number-2">1</span> Supplementary Requirements (the FURPS+) model</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-1">



</div>

<div id="outline-container-1-1" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="sec-1-1"><span class="section-number-3">1.1</span> Functionality</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-1-1">

<ul>
<li>The system must be able to create/edit/delete users.
</li>
<li>The system must be able to create/edit/delete/share documents.
</li>
<li>The system must keep a log of all document actions.
</li>
<li>All system usage requires user authentication.
</li>
</ul>

</div>

</div>

<div id="outline-container-1-2" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="sec-1-2"><span class="section-number-3">1.2</span> Usability</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-1-2">

<ul>
<li>The system must be easy to use.
<ul>
<li>Have a clean user interface.
</li>
<li>8 out of 10 users must be able to use the system without any training.
</li>
</ul>

</li>
<li>The system must be easily visible for people with "not perfect" vision. 
     E.g no graphics that blurs the view of the core system functionality.
</li>
<li>The web client must be easy and quick to navigate. No function should 
     be more than 3 clicks (windows/sub-windows) away.
<ul>
<li>Not counting navigating a users files.
</li>
</ul>

</li>
</ul>

</div>

</div>

<div id="outline-container-1-3" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="sec-1-3"><span class="section-number-3">1.3</span> Reliability</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-1-3">

<ul>
<li>The system must be able to recover from crashes.
</li>
<li>It must be possible to use the system without any internet connection.
<ul>
<li>With some limitations.
</li>
</ul>

</li>
</ul>

</div>

</div>

<div id="outline-container-1-4" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="sec-1-4"><span class="section-number-3">1.4</span> Performance</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-1-4">

<ul>
<li>The system must respond instantly
<ul>
<li>A request must not take more than a few (2-3) seconds.
</li>
<li>Not taking external factors (such as bad internet connection) into account.
</li>
</ul>

</li>
</ul>

</div>

</div>

<div id="outline-container-1-5" class="outline-3">
